About Us

About Us






Company Profile

Capital Bank operates 184 branches in Florida, North Carolina, South Carolina, Tennessee and Virginia. Through our branches, we offer a wide range of commercial and consumer loans and deposit products, as well as ancillary financial services.


Company Profile



Community Reinvestment Act (CRA)

Capital Bank is proud to be a member of the communities in which we operate.   Learn more about our commitment to meeting the credit needs of those communities.


Community Reinvestment Act (CRA)














